data.description: WELCOME to the epitome of luxury living in the prestigious Ballantrae Golf Neighborhood! This stunning residence boasts an inviting open concept design, featuring a master suite plus an additional bedroom on the main floor, ideal for multi-generational living or guests. The gourmet KITCHEN is a chef's delight with granite countertops, double ovens, and stainless steel appliances, perfect for preparing meals & entertaining. The main floor has gleaming hardwood floors and freshly painted walls.  Enjoy the tranquility of the sunroom nestled amidst lush trees, offering unparalleled privacy and a serene escape.  Upstairs you will find two bedrooms with a jack & jill bath.  Downstairs, a finished basement offers versatility with space for an office and a cozy den/man cave plus a full bath.  This meticulously maintained home offers comfort and entertaining.  The sound system is compatible w/ any receiver.  Grab your favorite Realtor and come see it for yourself.
